        <span style="color:#64748b">→</span>
        <span style="background:#22c55e;color:white;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600">Webhook</span>
        <span style="color:#64748b">→</span>
        <span style="background:#a855f7;color:white;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600">CRM (GHL)</span>
        <span style="color:#64748b">→</span>
        <span style="background:#032149;color:white;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600">Dashboard</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:16px">
      <div style="background:white;border-radius:12px;padding:18px;border:1px solid #e2e8f0">
        <p style="color:#032149;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px">Lo que guarda el CRM por lead:</p>
        <ul style="color:#64748b;font-size:13px;padding-left:16px;line-height:1.9;margin:0">
          <li><strong>Fuente:</strong> partner/influencer que lo trajo</li>
          <li><strong>Landing:</strong> URL de entrada</li>
          <li><strong>Fecha de registro</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Estado:</strong> registro → usuario activo → inversor</li>
          <li><strong>Importe invertido</strong> (cuando aplica)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div style="background:white;border-radius:12px;padding:18px;border:1px solid #e2e8f0">
        <p style="color:#032149;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px">Lo que permite calcular:</p>
        <ul style="color:#64748b;font-size:13px;padding-left:16px;line-height:1.9;margin:0">
